Hey, there! Thank you so much for
all your help the other day.

rows.label: tlk41310151_02_msg0002
rows.name:
After that, Dad went back
to Torigoth and started
living with my brothers.

rows.label: tlk41310151_02_msg0003
rows.name:
He even got a proper job... I
think Mom would be happy, too.
